snippet.title: The most ridiculous & hilarious ANIMAL moments #11 - Funny animal compilation - Watch & laugh!
snippet.description:
Animals and pets are so awesome and funny! There's so many funny animal moments that make us laugh! Just look how all these dogs, puppies, cats, kittens, goats, monkeys, cows, foxes, raccoons, ducks, birds, geese... behave, scare humans, sneeze, play, sleep and snore, fail, make funny sounds... So funny and cute! What is your favourite clip? :) Hope you like our compilation, please share it and SUBSCRIBE! Watch also our other videos!
